{"tid":1295594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【社福界報平安已核實頻道】","createTime":"2019-07-08T05:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T06:18:07.000Z","uid":267569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e6ef614db438a391777b081b1d4992cb5f321c32","tid":1295594,"uid":267569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:28:24.000Z","msg":"代轉<br />\n&lt;請廣傳&gt; 邀請大家subscribe【社福界報平安已核實頻道】<a href=\"https://t.me/HKpeace\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKpeace&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V5NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=8af90f0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKpeace</a><br />\n<br />\n＜頻道功能聲明＞<br />\n<br />\n本頻道已經與眾多社福界組織群結成通訊網，旨在統一並發佈社福界的第一手已核實消息，成為可靠的報平安平台，讓市民大眾能盡快得到已認證的消息。<br />\n<br />\n發佈消息類別：<br />\n1）已有社工在該區尋人的一手已核實消息<br />\n2）已確實並去除假消息<br />\n3）已有社工接觸到當事人的一手已核實消息<br />\n4）當事人已安全的一手已核實消息<br />\n*為保障前線工作，頻道不會公開跟進單位資料<br />\n*請體諒認證需時<br />\n<br />\n本頻道亦開放予熱心市民提供消息，報料：@lovinghkers_bot<br />\n請提供<br />\n✔️邊區邊件事✔️消息時間✔️消息來源 <br />\n❗️提供資料時請勿透露自己資料<br />\n<br />\n🇭🇰🇭🇰🇭🇰<br />\n香港人，這是我們的共同抗爭，也是需要休息接力的長路。正正因為一個都不能少，希望可以透過已認證的一手消息，讓大家安心照顧自己、互相守望。香港人，加油！"},{"pid":"1aba1103fe55286df78b31dd33d12671574c731d","tid":1295594,"uid":269622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:34:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa757005d4eab424082952164a7f6c9f9bfd245","tid":1295594,"uid":268327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S4X6zGM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS4X6zGM.png&h=a721d437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人要團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似蟲蟲特工隊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蟲蟲特攻隊 - 香港人Version<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295142\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295142</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫手推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3060fc96a9ff4cae45803d14dc4fa00aca261f4c","tid":1295594,"uid":84088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:18:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}